
how to create new network docker
docker network create mongo-network
how to network 
docker network ls


how to mongo and mongo express connection 
we need pull two images 1. mongo 2. mongo-express
docker pull mongo
docker pull mongo-express

we need run mongo with network created and environmental variable pass using port mapping.

 docker run -d --network mongo-network --name mongo -p 27017:27017 \
	-e MONGO_INITDB_ROOT_USERNAME=admin \
	-e MONGO_INITDB_ROOT_PASSWORD=password \
	mongo

URL Link here we need to follow.

https://gitlab.com/nanuchi/techworld-js-docker-demo-app





